{
  "texts": [
    "Notably, the trend for Vaccine CTs increased leading up to the emergence of COVID-19 in 2019, and the two exhibited a similar pattern after that.",
    "Before the COVID-19 pandemic, Vaccine CTs often revolved around other viruses such as Ebola, HIV, and Polio.",
    "However, after the emergence of COVID-19, Vaccine CTs primarily focused on the COVID-19 vaccine.As shown in Fig.13, the frequency of QAnon CTs increased after the emergence of COVID-19 in late 2020, which was one year after the initial appearance of COVID-19.",
    "According to Morelock et al. [82], there is a connection between QAnon and COVID-19 CTs, as people are finding it difficult to trust the information they receive and are becoming less interested in learning from experts.",
    "These ideas are being spread on the Internet, and QAnon took advantage of the COVID-19 situation to increase its popularity."
  ]
}